azin=2C 1946 (Photograph: Henri Cartier-Bresson/Magnum)<br></p><p style=3D=
"-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #262626;=
font-family: Georgia=2C serif;font-size: 15px;line-height: 175%;text-align=
: left;">Three days before his forty-second birthday=2C Kazin writes:</p><=
blockquote style=3D"-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;-ms-text-size-adjust: 1=
