orgia=2C serif;font-size: 15px;line-height: 175%;text-align: left;">Pulsar=
s =E2=80=94 enormous=2C rapidly spinning=2C extremely dense spheres of nuc=
lear matter magnetized with a strength exceeding Earth=E2=80=99s magnetic=
